f minimizing portfolio risk through arbitrage investing and maintaining cash reserves during challenging markets effectively preserved assets during this difficult period going forward we continue to strive to maximize returns while minimizing market risk the funds daily net asset value is available in the financial press and each evening after  pm eastern time by calling gabelli  the funds nasdaq symbol is gabcx please call us during the business day for further information sincerely s mario j gabelli mario j gabelli cfa portfolio manager and chief investment officer october   top ten holdings september   lone star industries inc wicor inc nielsen media research inc commnet cellular inc nalco chemical co thermo power corp cilcorp inc southwest gas corp furon co united water resources inc note the views expressed in this report reflect those of the portfolio manager only through the end of the period stated in this report the managers views are subject to change at any time based on market and other conditions  the gambelli abc fund portfolio of investments  september   unaudited  market shares value   common stocks   automotive parts and accessories    federalmogul corp     aviation parts and services    aviall inc    fairchild corp cl a    hishear industries inc    kaman corp cl a      broadcasting    salem communications corp cl a    liberty corp      building and construction    lone star industries inc    business services    fisher scientific international inc    national processing inc    nielsen media research inc    procurenet inc      communications equipment    dynatech corp    l   communications holdings inc      computer software and services    decisionone holdings corp    consumer products    carterwallace inc    general housewares corp    syratech corp      diversified industrial    ampcopittsburgh corp    furon co    katy industries inc    thermo power corp    whx corp      electronics    ucar international inc    energy and utilities    agl resourc